IN THE PARKING LOT

00:12:01,020 --> 00:12:02,155
TRYING TO MEET
THE UPPER MANAGEMENT.

00:12:02,155 --> 00:12:04,424
I INTRODUCED THEM TO
THE UPPER MANAGEMENT, AND BAM!

00:12:04,424 --> 00:12:06,292
THE ORDER
FINALLY WENT THROUGH.

00:12:06,292 --> 00:12:07,393
A TOAST?! HEY, HEY, HEY!
CHEERS!

00:12:07,393 --> 00:12:11,064
WE'RE FORTUNATE TO BE
ABLE TO LIVE THE AMERICAN DREAM,

00:12:11,064 --> 00:12:12,298
COOKING
THE AMERICAN CUISINE.

00:12:12,298 --> 00:12:15,435
THERE'S NOTHING MORE AMERICAN
THAN TWO GUYS WITH A GOOD IDEA

00:12:15,435 --> 00:12:18,204
AND REALLY BEING ABLE TO CREATE
SOMETHING FROM NOTHING.

00:12:27,981 --> 00:12:31,317
Narrator: NEXT UP IS A BUSINESS
