SnagaStool IS
THE FIRST AND ONLY MOBILE APP

00:13:01,147 --> 00:13:03,416
THAT ENSURES YOU'LL GET THE
BEST SEAT AT YOUR FAVORITE BAR.

00:13:03,416 --> 00:13:05,285
AT THE BAR,
YOU GET THE BEST SERVICE,

00:13:05,285 --> 00:13:08,021
THE BEST VIEW
OF THE TV,

00:13:08,021 --> 00:13:09,122
AND YOU GET TO TALK
TO THE BARTENDER.

00:13:09,122 --> 00:13:11,124
BUT AS WE ALL KNOW,
SOMETIMES IT'S IMPOSSIBLE

00:13:11,124 --> 00:13:13,293
TO GET A SEAT
AT THE BAR.

00:13:13,293 --> 00:13:15,461
NATURALLY, WE THOUGHT, "THERE'S
GOT TO BE AN APP FOR THAT."

00:13:15,461 --> 00:13:18,264
BUT THERE WASN'T,
SO WE CREATED ONE.

00:13:18,264 --> 00:13:21,401
NOW, WITH SnagaStool, YOU SIMPLY
PICK YOUR FAVORITE BAR --

00:13:21,401 --> 00:13:23,169
LIKE THE SHARK TANK
BAR AND GRILL.

00:13:23,169 --> 00:13:26,072
THEY MAKE A-A MEAN
"MARK CUBAN" LIBRE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:13:26,072 --> 00:13:29,142
YOU COULD SELECT
THE DATE AND THE TIME

00:13:29,142 --> 00:13:31,144
AND THE NUMBER
OF BAR STOOLS,

00:13:31,144 --> 00:13:33,079
AND YOU GET TO SNAG
THE BEST SEAT IN THE HOUSE.

00:13:37,083 --> 00:13:39,218
BARS LOVE SnagaStool.

00:13:39,218 --> 00:13:43,222
IT CREATES NEW OPPORTUNITIES
TO FILL OFF-PEAK TIMES,

00:13:43,222 --> 00:13:46,359
TO ATTRACT NEW CUSTOMERS,
AND TO CREATE LIFELONG FANS.

00:13:46,359 --> 00:13:50,029
WE'VE CREATED AN INCREDIBLE
CUSTOMER EXPERIENCE,

00:13:50,029 --> 00:13:52,365
AND WE'VE PROVEN THAT
WITH SOME AMAZING BARS.

00:13:52,365 --> 00:13:55,268
SO, THE ONLY QUESTION
WE HAVE LEFT, SHARKS --

00:13:55,268 --> 00:13:56,436
WHO WANTS
TO SNAG A STOOL?!

00:13:56,436 --> 00:14:00,273
WHY DO I NEED YOU?
YOU SAID "OFF-PEAK TIMES."

00:14:00,273 --> 00:14:02,008
IF I OWN THE BAR
AND IT'S OFF-PEAK,

00:14:02,008 --> 00:14:03,142
THE BAR STOOL IS EMPTY
ANYWAY.

00:14:03,142 --> 00:14:05,311
YOU DON'T
NEED TO RESERVE IT.

00:14:05,311 --> 00:14:07,246
IF THE BAR IS
SUPER-BUSY,

00:14:07,246 --> 00:14:10,249
WHAT'S THE BENEFIT TO ME
TO LEAVE THE BAR STOOL EMPTY

00:14:10,249 --> 00:14:11,351
WAITING FOR YOU?

00:14:11,351 --> 00:14:13,186
SOMEONE'S ALWAYS GONNA
SIT IN IT.

00:14:13,186 --> 00:14:14,287
THAT'S RIGHT.

00:14:14,287 --> 00:14:16,456
SO, THERE ARE TWO TIME PERIODS
ON SnagaStool,

00:14:16,456 --> 00:14:19,025
AND WE'VE --
WE'VE IDENTIFIED THOSE

00:14:19,025 --> 00:14:21,361
AS "PEAK TIMES"
AND "OFF-PEAK TIMES."
OKAY.

00:14:21,361 --> 00:14:22,395
AND DURING
THE OFF-PEAK TIMES,

00:14:22,395 --> 00:14:24,364
THAT'S WHEN BARS
WILL OFFER INCENTIVES,

00:14:24,364 --> 00:14:27,200
LIKE A FREE BEER
OR A FREE APPETIZER,

00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,969
TO ATTRACT PEOPLE TO THEIR BAR
TO FILL THOSE STOOLS.

00:14:29,969 --> 00:14:32,038
OKAY, SO, I GO ON YOUR APP,
I GET A FREE BEER?
THAT'S RIGHT.

00:14:32,038 --> 00:14:34,006
AND THE ADVANTAGE TO THE BAR
IS THEY GET CUSTOMERS IN

00:14:34,006 --> 00:14:36,109
WHEN IT'S NOT BUSY.
ABSOLUTELY.

00:14:36,109 --> 00:14:38,945
I COULD SEE, LIKE, PEOPLE JUST
REALLY BEING PISSED OFF...

00:14:38,945 --> 00:14:41,381
IF THEY GO
INTO THEIR FAVORITE BAR...
YEAH.

00:14:41,381 --> 00:14:42,949
...IT'S JAM-PACKED...
MM-HMM.

00:14:42,949 --> 00:14:44,384
...AND THERE'S TWO SIGNS
LIKE THAT ON THE STOOLS.

00:14:44,384 --> 00:14:47,253
Cuban: I COULD SEE
HAVING THOSE THERE

00:14:47,253 --> 00:14:48,421
COULD BE LIKE --
MAKE IT INTERESTING, RIGHT?

00:14:48,421 --> 00:14:50,323
"WHO'S COMING? WHO'S COMING?
IT'S RESERVED."

00:14:50,323 --> 00:14:52,158
JUST LIKE WHEN YOU SEE
RESERVED TABLES.

00:14:52,158 --> 00:14:55,261
I'M FROM BOSTON, OKAY? I'VE
NEVER HEARD OF THIS, ALL RIGHT?

00:14:55,261 --> 00:14:57,196
LET'S TALK ABOUT
THE EL SUPREMO BAR STOOL --

00:14:57,196 --> 00:15:02,335
UPSTAIRS BAR, GRILL 23,
PATS GAME ON A SUNDAY.

00:15:02,335 --> 00:15:04,137
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
FOR ME THERE?

00:15:04,137 --> 00:15:06,139
I'M NOT HAVING ANY TROUBLE
FILLING THAT BAR.

00:15:06,139 --> 00:15:08,975
