FOR TWO HOURS TO KEEP MY SEAT.

00:15:13,413 --> 00:15:15,248
IS THERE ANY WAY
I CAN USE YOUR APP

00:15:15,248 --> 00:15:18,184
TO RESERVE MY SEAT
15 MINUTES BEFORE GAME TIME?

00:15:18,184 --> 00:15:22,188
IT DEPENDS ON IF THE BAR HAS
ENOUGH INVENTORY OF STOOLS

00:15:22,188 --> 00:15:24,490
AND IF THEY HAVEN'T
BEEN SNAGGED UP TO THAT POINT.

00:15:24,490 --> 00:15:27,160
'CAUSE THEY ALLOCATE
A CERTAIN AMOUNT FOR YOU?
THAT'S RIGHT.

00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:29,228
NOT ALL BAR STOOLS ARE --
ARE OPEN FOR THE SERVICE.

00:15:29,228 --> 00:15:32,131
PEOPLE ARE WILLING TO PAY
FOR THIS EXPERIENCE.

00:15:32,131 --> 00:15:34,300
SO, FOR PEOPLE
WHO AREN'T ABLE TO

00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:36,269
GET TO THE BAR
TWO OR THREE HOURS EARLY --

00:15:36,269 --> 00:15:37,437
PEOPLE
WHO ARE WORKING LATE,

00:15:37,437 --> 00:15:39,272
PEOPLE WHO DON'T HAVE
THE ABILITY TO SIT

00:15:39,272 --> 00:15:41,007
AND NURSE A BEER
FOR HOURS --

00:15:41,007 --> 00:15:43,042
THESE BARS NOW HAVE
THE ABILITY TO PROVIDE --

00:15:43,042 --> 00:15:44,977
SO, HOW DO YOU CHARGE?
HOW DO YOU CHARGE?

00:15:44,977 --> 00:15:46,446
SO, WE CHARGE BY THE HOUR
OR BY THE GAME,

00:15:46,446 --> 00:15:49,215
DEPENDING ON WHAT THE BAR
WOULD LIKE TO CHARGE.
OKAY, SO, GIVE ME AN EXAMPLE.

00:15:49,215 --> 00:15:51,417
YEAH, SO -- SO, RIGHT NOW,
WE'VE PARTNERED

00:15:51,417 --> 00:15:53,319
WITH SOME AMAZING BARS
IN THE BOSTON AREA.

00:15:53,319 --> 00:15:56,088
HOW MANY?
SO, RIGHT NOW,
WE'RE WITH THREE BARS.

00:15:56,088 --> 00:15:57,089
AND THAT'S WHAT --
THREE?

00:15:57,089 --> 00:15:59,158
THREE BARS.
YEP. YEP.

00:15:59,158 --> 00:16:01,360
GUYS, I GET YOU GOT TO CRAWL
BEFORE YOU BALL.
YEAH.

00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:03,062
BUT WHY
JUST THREE BARS?

00:16:03,062 --> 00:16:05,298
SO, WE JUST WANTED TO START OFF
WITH A PILOT,

00:16:05,298 --> 00:16:06,365
AND WE REALLY WANTED TO
PARTNER WITH PEOPLE

00:16:06,365 --> 00:16:08,067
WHO REALLY BELIEVED
IN THE CONCEPT.

00:16:08,067 --> 00:16:11,204
WE'RE NOT GONNA TAKE REVENUE
FROM THESE BECAUSE --

00:16:11,204 --> 00:16:12,371
ALL RIGHT.
YOU HAVE NO SALES.

00:16:12,371 --> 00:16:14,006
LITTLE LESS.
IT'S -- IT'S OUR
PROOF OF CONCEPT.

00:16:14,006 --> 00:16:17,043
THERE ARE SO MANY APPS
RIGHT NOW DESIGNED FOR BARS.

00:16:17,043 --> 00:16:19,245
WHY ARE THEY EVEN
GOING TO DEAL WITH YOU

00:16:19,245 --> 00:16:21,080
WHEN YOU'RE JUST
ONE OF 50 APPS

00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:23,082
THAT ARE --
THAT ARE APPROACHING THEM?

00:16:23,082 --> 00:16:24,250
SO, MARK,
IN -- IN OUR OPINION,

00:16:24,250 --> 00:16:27,153
THE -- THE ART OF BARTENDING
HAS DIED SLOWLY.

00:16:27,153 --> 00:16:29,255
WE'RE TRYING TO
GET BACK TO THE DAYS

00:16:29,255 --> 00:16:30,323
WHEN A BARTENDER
REACHED ACROSS THE BAR

00:16:30,323 --> 00:16:32,458
AND KNEW YOUR NAME,
KNEW WHO YOU WERE.

00:16:32,458 --> 00:16:34,260
DON'T DISM--
YOU BETTER ROLL UP YOUR
PANT LEGS WHEN YOU SAY THAT,

00:16:34,260 --> 00:16:35,428
RIGHT, BECAUSE --
DON'T DISMISS THIS,

00:16:35,428 --> 00:16:36,462
BECAUSE IT MEANS A LOT.

00:16:36,462 --> 00:16:38,231
BECAUSE THAT'S
HOW YOU BUILD LOYALTY

00:16:38,231 --> 00:16:40,299
IS BY PROVIDING
AN ENHANCED CUSTOMER SERVICE.

00:16:40,299 --> 00:16:42,268
YEAH, BUT THAT'S NOT
WHAT YOU'RE SELLING, THOUGH.
IT'S NOT --

00:16:42,268 --> 00:16:44,103
O'Leary: EXCEPT, YOU KNOW,
THERE'S SOMETHING INTRIGUING

00:16:44,103 --> 00:16:45,271
ABOUT YOUR CONCEPT
BECAUSE THERE'S

00:16:45,271 --> 00:16:48,007
PROBABLY 25 STOOLS
UPSTAIRS AT GRILL 23,

00:16:48,007 --> 00:16:51,077
ANOTHER 40 DOWNSTAIRS
AT THE DOWNSTAIRS BAR.

00:16:51,077 --> 00:16:53,379
THEY ARE THE MOST COVETED SEATS
FOR ANY GAME IN BOSTON.

00:16:53,379 --> 00:16:55,948
SO, WHY DO THEY NEED THEM?
BUT WAIT. HERE ME OUT ON THIS.

00:16:55,948 --> 00:16:58,050
IF I COULD GO TO THEM SAY,

00:16:58,050 --> 00:17:00,086
"LOOK, GIVE ME
20% OF YOUR INVENTORY,

00:17:00,086 --> 00:17:03,022
AND I'LL GUARANTEE YOU
$200 FOR THAT SEAT."

00:17:03,022 --> 00:17:06,025
BUT KEVIN'S ALMOST RIGHT, RIGHT?
AND HE'S --
HE'S ALWAYS RIGHT.

00:17:06,025 --> 00:17:08,461
[ CHUCKLES ]
