THE VALUE THAT YOU BRING.

00:17:20,373 --> 00:17:22,141
WELL, YOU HAVE A GUARANTEED
REVENUE STREAM, THEN.

00:17:22,141 --> 00:17:23,175
RIGHT, IT'S NEWFOUND REVENUE.
THAT'S THE ONLY REASON
THEY'D DO IT.

00:17:23,175 --> 00:17:24,310
