BUT YOU HAVEN'T SHOWN
A WAY TO SELL THAT VALUE.

00:17:36,289 --> 00:17:38,424
AND BECAUSE YOU HAVEN'T BEEN
ABLE TO FIGURE THAT OUT,

00:17:38,424 --> 00:17:41,160
I'M OUT.

00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:43,162
I'M NOT A BAR GUY,
AND I CAN'T HELP YOU IN THIS.

00:17:43,162 --> 00:17:44,196
I'M OUT.

00:17:44,196 --> 00:17:46,265
[ LAUGHS ]

